OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSri Lanka plans to pay off 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FIran oil debt with tea     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Sri Lanka plans to settle a debt for   
OL,6, past oil imports from Iran by paying it
OL,7, off in tea, a government minister said.
OL,9,FRamesh Pathirana said his country hoped
OL,10,Fto send $5m (#3.8m) worth of tea to    
OL,11,FIran each month to clear a $251m debt. 
OL,13,FSri Lanka is experiencing a severe debt
OL,14,Fand foreign exchange crisis, which has 
OL,15,Fbeen made worse by the loss of tourist 
OL,16,Fincome during the coronavirus pandemic.
OL,18,FA member of the country's tea board    
OL,19,Fsaid it was the first time tea had been
OL,20,Fbartered to settle foreign debt.       
